  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to determine whether thyroid hormone levels are predictive of cardiac
      remodeling following myocardial infarction and the prognosis in patients with STEMI receiving
      primary percutaneous coronary intervention.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
